posts.name: Ethan Reed
posts.cooked:
Here’s my data from the top 20 teams in champs qualifications, sorted by average teleop cargo scored:

image 1280×448 60.8 KB

image 1280×448 60.8 KB

image 1280×448 60.8 KB

The final column is an attempt to determine how many more or fewer cargo a team caused their partners to score, calculated by their cargo OPR divided by 2, minus their actual cargo average.

I generated this list of teams by looking at my best guess for the top 50 teams, determined by:

Top 4 OPRs in each division (24)

Captain/first pick of every alliance in division finals (9)

High OPRs not yet accounted for (17)

And then sorting by teleop cargo scored, and truncating at 20.
